               <div class="content">
              <div itemprop="articleBody"><p><strong>Higher Education Online Admissions and Enrolment Procedure&nbsp;</strong><strong>for 1<sup>st</sup>&nbsp; Semester SY 2022-2023<br></strong>*Returnees and 2<sup>nd</sup> Undergraduate Degree Applicants of XU</p><p><strong>*RETURNEES</strong> refer to Xavier Ateneo upperclassmen who did not enroll during the previous semester(s)&nbsp;and will re-enroll in the incoming semester.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step1</strong><br><strong>1.1 </strong>Access this link: <a href="https://forms.gle/qmdjs6SfV22qHPb47">https://forms.gle/qmdjs6SfV22qHPb47</a> to register in the evaluation process for&nbsp;<strong>2<sup>nd</sup> UNDERGRADUATE DEGREE APPLICANTS </strong><em>who earned their first undergraduate degree at Xavier Ateneo</em>. IMPORTANT: the above link is for applicants to programs <span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a href="/accepted-undergrad/admission-listcourseswaived">listed</a></span> under waived entrance exam.</p><ul> <li><em>For XU graduates applying to programs with entrance exam requirement</em>, kindly accomplish the steps indicated <span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a href="/admission-takers-passers">here</a></span>.</li> <li><em>For applicants who earned their first undergraduate degree in another school</em>, if applying to a program with entrance exam requirement, kindly click <span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a href="/admission-takers-passers">here</a> </span>for the steps. If to a program listed under waived, click <span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a href="/admission-waivedenrollment">here</a></span>.</li> </ul><p><strong>1.2 </strong>Access this link <a href="https://forms.gle/4AnG9YDPvTVWqp557">https://forms.gle/4AnG9YDPvTVWqp557</a> to register in the evaluation process for <strong>RETURNEES</strong></p><p><strong>Step2<br>2.1 </strong><strong>For Graduates of Xavier Ateneo: </strong>After <em>successful</em> evaluation, applicants will be emailed their unique <strong>REGISTRATION NUMBER </strong>by the University Testing Center. This Registration number will be used in creating an account in the online admissions portal: <a href="http://apply.xu.edu.ph/">http://apply.xu.edu.ph/</a></p><p>An <strong>ADMISSIONS CLEARANCE</strong> will be emailed to successfully processed applicants.&nbsp;Kindly check both the <strong>INBOX</strong> and <strong>SPAM</strong> folders of the email account registered in&nbsp;the online admissions portal.</p><p><strong>2.2 </strong><strong>For Returnees</strong>: After <em>successful</em> evaluation, applicants will be emailed a&nbsp;<strong>RETURNEEâ€™s ADMISSIONS CLEARANCE. </strong>Kindly check both the <strong>INBOX</strong> and <strong>SPAM</strong> folders&nbsp;of the email account used during registration.</p><p><strong>Step3<br></strong>Pay the required down payment of Php3,000.00<br>Go to this link <a href="/payment-centers-finance">https://www.xu.edu.ph/payment-centers-finance</a> to view the list of accredited&nbsp;XU payment centers.</p><ul> <li><strong>IMPORTANT: </strong>Use your Campus ID Number + Full Name as the reference number when filling out the bank forms.</li> </ul><p><strong>Step4<br></strong>Process <strong>Online Enrollment Registration</strong> of your school/college by accessing the link:</p><p style="padding-left: 2em;"><a href="/admissions-enrollment">https://www.xu.edu.ph/admissions-enrollment</a>.</p><p>Prepare clear scanned copies or photo of the following requirements:</p><p style="padding-left: 2em;">a) Admissions Clearance<br>b) Validated Down Payment Deposit slip<br>c) PSA Birth Certificate (2<sup>nd</sup> courser only)</p><ul> <li>After completing the online registration, a notification will be sent to you via email&nbsp;regarding the status of your application for enrollment in XU. If successful, you will&nbsp;be given your Login credentials to access the Student Lifecycle Management and&nbsp;Information System (SLMIS) to check your class schedule and other related information.</li> </ul><di